    "However, as shown in Fig. 1, these approaches often rely heavily on full white-box access to target models or extensive knowledge of fundamental generative model principles.",
    "Specifically, the design of existing methods fundamentally requiring U-Net participation alongside Text Encoder and (optionally) VAE Decoder.",
